/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不如從頭黎過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f959c8efd6d0312446f59fba388dd7e9cdefb08","tid":578624,"uid":169807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T23:13:09.000Z","msg":"爺夜深時曾經問心<br />\n有沒有太過傷害別人<br />\n才發覺世事總有原因<br />\n沒有爺她們學不到死心<br />\n<br />\n爺是她們要修的行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"255cd6cbd1cbbcf01f5cb0a9c0eb577b8d68a121","tid":578624,"uid":10968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T23:40:11.000Z","msg":"直接講分手<br />\n唔洗同佢嘈 直接block 晒佢可以搵到你既途徑"},{"pid":"a9f958d6f333829cebb72b46037efc49623f17c3","tid":578624,"uid":132674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T23:44:53.000Z","msg":"不如算啦"},{"pid":"033a9dad3b7d719a4999990068b08784e195414d","tid":578624,"uid":151780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T23:47:37.000Z","msg":"要死一早死咗 照分 <br />\n最憎呢啲拎生命要脅對方嘅垃圾"},{"pid":"ea0a3de0b61efdf6853c3eaee949f02082d02f54","tid":578624,"uid":165980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T01:33:19.000Z","msg":"block柒晒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}